==Mandarin==

===Etymology===
Literally: One minute blue, and the next minute white.

===Pronunciation===
[[Pinyin]]: yī zhèn qīng yī zhèn bái

===Phrase===
'''[[一阵]][[青]][[一阵]][[白]]''' ([[Simplified Chinese]])

# (''idiom'') Describes the change someone's facial expression when they become surpirsed or angry.

